  - m_Id: 42674803449352192
    m_Localized: GAME
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43745364648742912
    m_Localized: Before you begin
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43745421045354496
    m_Localized: 1. Put on the EEG headset
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43745640935936000
    m_Localized: Wear your EEG headset and confirm the signal is stable before starting.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43746019111161856
    m_Localized: 2. Sit comfortably and stay still
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43746564936912896
    m_Localized: How to play
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43746756348170240
    m_Localized: Use the arrow keys to move your airplane balloon up and down.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43747437121458176
    m_Localized: Fly through the ring to earn points.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43747549356838912
    m_Localized: Avoid the bomb.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43747706651627520
    m_Localized: "You have 300 trials \u2014 stay focused for the whole session."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43748679876956160
    m_Localized: Easy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43748707811020800
    m_Localized: Slow pace, easy to react.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43748796327612416
    m_Localized: Medium
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43748823896772608
    m_Localized: Faster objects, stay alert.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43748878733103104
    m_Localized: Hard
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43748944210382848
    m_Localized: Very fast, full focus needed.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43749662212313088
    m_Localized: Difficulty adjusts automatically based on your performance.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43749797809967104
    m_Localized: Your attention level is tracked throughout the session via the EEG
      headset.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43751981217828864
    m_Localized: Minimize movement during the session to keep EEG readings accurate.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43748303228456960
    m_Localized: Difficulty levels
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43774741180665856
    m_Localized: Press Space only when the Square appears above the cross.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43775432301301760
    m_Localized: Do not press anything for anything else.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43775600639692800
    m_Localized: Try to stay quick and accurate.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43775629282594816
    m_Localized: Continue until the task ends.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43788511311384576
    m_Localized: A stimulus appears briefly above or below the cross.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43788626965123072
    m_Localized: Press Space only when the coffee appears above the cross.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43788787384668160
    m_Localized: Do not press anything for anything else.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43788884226953216
    m_Localized: "You have 300 trials \u2014 stay focused for the whole session."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43790578453139456
    m_Localized: Coffee only, stay alert.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43790687173693440
    m_Localized: Other objects added, full focus needed.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43810498427572224
    m_Localized: Unfocus Indicator
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43810576420655104
    m_Localized: Focus Indicator
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43901797675651072
    m_Localized: Quit Game
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
